ou help the developers to continue to add more features by having more funds for this beautiful product and they also reward you by giving you all the present and future heroes that will be added in the game for free,FOREVER, even the heroes added after the game leaves Early Access, without having to unlock them through gameplay or by in-game currency.I truly recommend this game for all kind of audience, even if you don't like this kind of genre, it will sure get to you and eventually you will F***ing love it!"
