,Recommended,504370,25621874,"Posted: 21 September, 2016",all,Qelris,"This game should be the litteral definition of MOBA. It is multiplayer game where you fight online in a battle arena. No lanes. No bushes. No level ups. Just straight Multiplayer Online Battle Arena.The game features Casual/Ranked 2v2/3v3, Private Matches with a few custom options, Play vs AIs for your Daily Quests needs when you're lazy and a Playground where you can go test the skills and battlerites of any Champions. The Playground is very important and everyone that plays this game should visit this place every so often, especially the newer players, so they can get a quick feeling of everyone's skills. As for ranked, ranks are split between solo and the different teams you play with. That means that you could be Gold 2 solo, but Diamond 5 with Bob, and Platinum 6 with Bob and Martin.Matches are best 3 of out 5 rounds(around 8 to 12 minutes per match). Each round, the game gives you 3 pre-determined Battlerites, depending on the current round, to choose from(2 on round 5, for your ultimate). Battlerites slightly alter one of your skills. While certain choices look very strong on paper, it doesn't mean it will be your best option agaisnt your current opponents.The game currently features 21 Champions split through 3 categories: 7 Melees, 7 Rangeds, 7 Supports. While some Champions share similar skill mechanics, they feel different to play due to the rest of their skill kits.Recently, they added Campaign, which is just an extended Tutorial. The name chosen aside, it does a great job at explaining everything you need to know before you start playing agaisnt humans. Now players that go through the Campaign will know what EX-Skills are.The game is meant to go Free to Play later on, but if you buy it right now, you will gain access to all Champions and future released Champions.The game also has a DLC that isn't listed on the store page. While the value of the Ultimate Fan Pack is often argued about, if you have spare money and want to support Stunlock Studio further, you can get some exclusive things. Buying the Ultimate Fan Pack gives you the Battle Wolf mount, the Goblin Throne mount and Permanent 10% EXP gain for the price of 30$ USD/33$ CDN. Personally, I value the Ultimate Fan Pack more than buying Gold Chests, because over time, assuming you play the game, you will be able to get a lot of the cosmetics through Silver Chests and weekly Gold Chests."
