76561198089925383,Recommended,504370,25699688,"Posted: 25 September, 2016",all,EasY,"Reading this keep in mind reviewer literally spent years on almost every popular MOBA to date.First things first this game is so flawless you can hardly say it belongs in Early Access. It's a great arena brawler that is easy to learn but incredibly hard to master. In my humble opinion this game has much harder pvp than Dota 2 or LoL. There are no target skills, you have to land everything manually, which means pure skill. You have 2 currencies gold with which you buy chests, or get them by lvl up or doing daily quests. The loot system in this game is pretty much the same as overwatch. You get chests and each has three items.  If you get a duplicate, then it gets cashed out in crystals which is second currency. With crystals you can buy anything right now (All skins). That pretty much sums it up.People say game will come out as f2p title in 2017, but if you buy now you get all characters for free even future ones. One more thing to mention is every character is effective even on very high elo, game is very balanced in my opinion no ""useless characters"". Definitely would recommend this game."
