76561198042042167,Recommended,504370,25916658,"Posted: 7 October, 2016",all,Linttle,"Simply put, it's a MOBA without any laning, pushing and farming mechanics. Right from the start, you're thrust into fighting enemy champions immediately (and only enemy champions). What's so great about this game is that it's all about skillshots and rewards fast reaction (through counters and escapes) and there's no crit chance modifiers or hit procs. So it really rewards players with a high skill level. From what I've played so far, there's no champion that's completely OP and how strong some champions are can really differ from player to player based on their level of skill.If you like a hero brawler that's about instant action and feels pretty much balanced, this is the game for you. Note that it'll go free-to-play someday, so you don't necessarily have to buy it."
