ing my vibe. So if you're a new player keep the chat disabled. Trust me. You'll have more fun.At the end of the day I think this isn't the game for me. I'm not enjoying it. I find it very difficult for me to get used to the camera angle. I don't like any of the characters they have available (I've tried them all). I wouldn't recommend this unless you're used to playing games like Dota 2 or League of Legends and want something more fast pace. I also wouldn't recommend this if you play alone a lot like I do."
